So all the *dsLoadBalancer.shutdown() (e.g. CdsLoadBalancer.shutdown) have this:
  public void shutdown() {
    logger.log(XdsLogLevel.INFO, "Shutdown");
...
}

Agreed XdsLogLevel.INFO is not the same as Level.INFO  but they all say "Shutdown" so being consistent. I am changing from INFO to FINER .

